OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fspreading northeast during the
OL,7,Fmorning. The rain will be mainly light
OL,8,Fbut a few isolated heavy showers may
OL,9,Fdevelop in the southwest in the
OL,10,Fafternoon along with a few brighter
OL,11,Fspells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA few bright spells and
OL,14,Fisolated heavy showers at first.
OL,15,FOtherwise cloudy with patchy rain in
OL,16,Fthe evening, clearing east overnight.
OL,17,FFurther cloud and rain in the
OL,18,Fsouthwest by morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
