OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBreezy and mostly cloudy
OL,6,Fthroughout the day as outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain move east, these heavy at times.
OL,8,FStaying driest and brightest towards
OL,9,FEast Lothian and Berwickshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FLargely dry with bright or sunny
OL,13,Fspells on Monday morning, a few
OL,14,Fshowers in the afternoon. Bright or
OL,15,Fsunny spells and scattered showers
OL,16,FTuesday and Wednesday, some heavy and
OL,17,Fthundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
